WEBVTT

00:00:57.640 --> 00:01:01.226
the answer would be
Delhi, Mumbai, Kolkata.

00:01:01.250 --> 00:01:03.598
You'd immediately ask again:

00:01:04.370 --> 00:01:06.933
"Where do you belong?"

00:01:07.410 --> 00:01:11.615
Until recently in India,
nobody was from a city;

00:01:12.170 --> 00:01:14.226
people only migrated to the city.

00:01:14.250 --> 00:01:15.627
This is changing.

00:01:16.570 --> 00:01:19.401
Urbanization is changing India,

00:01:20.290 --> 00:01:22.450
but are our cities prepared?

00:01:23.690 --> 00:01:25.860
Let's assume you were born somewhere else.

00:01:26.170 --> 00:01:30.782
Your parents worked as laborers all day.